text: Sara Li (born Sara Linnea Larsson; 30 March 1988 in Ystad) is a Swedish singer. Sara Li was a member of the popgroup Sheelah (originally known as Caracola) from 2009 to 2010, and she participated in Melodifestivalen in the year of 2012 along with Björn Ranelid with the song "Mirakel". They reached the final of Melodifestivalen from the semifinal which took place on 12 February 2012 in leksand, the semifinal was broadcast on Sveriges Television. In the final in Globen Arena their song placed 10th receiving the sixth highest televote result.Björn Ranelid och Sara Li på sista plats svt.se Retrieved 22 March 2017 The same year she participated in television singing show Så ska det låta, teaming up with singer Patrik Isaksson.
